name: AOM3 Based Giantess LoRA
description:
The LoRA was trained using 20 giantess images I have generated using AOM3 last week.

It is capable of creating female characters at/over building heights. The trigger word is "GiantessC" and best fits with "from above" or "from above" camera angles.

I have tested the LoRA with the following models without merging:
AnythingV3 - Good
Any versions of Orange Mixes - Good
Chilloutmix - Okay
deliberate_v11 - Very Good
Elysium_Anime_V3 - Okay
Kenshi - Okay

Update 01:
It seems deliberate_v11 gives the BEST results in terms of raw model.
(see images with crowded village)

Make sure to have "height difference" or "size difference" to increase the chance of generating.

Update 02:
Replace images with newly generated ones using controlnet.

Disclaimer:
Depending on your model mix / prompt structures, outputs may vary and the chances of giantess occurrences may not be 100%. (Roughly 70% work on my test cases).
